    - target: {fileID: 8045659150639517358, guid: fbcc40e91526859428bab09db558e208, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_value.<Text>k__BackingField
      value: '[determined] Ah, my friend, my adventures began on a misty dawn when
        I first picked up my sword. [reflective] Through countless battles, I have
        faced fierce enemies and witnessed the chaos of medieval warfare. [confident]
        Each victory and defeat has shaped me into the warrior I am today, eager
        to share tales of bravery and cunning. [proud] There''s nothing quite like
        the thrill of defending my homeland and standing tall amidst the chaos of
        battle.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
